<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Sectors</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Industrial &amp; Logistics</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Warehouses, distribution centres and big-box units run to the minute — so the building services that keep them running have to be fast, robust and built at scale. We bring MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works together under one accountable team, sized for large spans and tight programmes. From a new-build shed to a recladding or power upgrade, one project manager owns the date.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Industrial &amp; Logistics →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Across every trade</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Four service lines,<br>under one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>High-bay &amp; warehouse lighting with controls</li><li>Power distribution, sub-mains &amp; EV charging</li><li>Heating, ventilation &amp; destratification</li><li>Fire alarm &amp; sprinkler coordination</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Office pods, welfare &amp; amenity space</li><li>Mezzanines &amp; racking-ready floors</li><li>Trade-counter &amp; showroom fit-out</li><li>Robust, hard-wearing finishes</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Large-span roofing &amp; roof refurbishment</li><li>Cladding, recladding &amp; overcladding</li><li>Dock levellers, doors &amp; loading openings</li><li>Weatherproofing &amp; thermal upgrades to Part L</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Yards &amp; HGV hardstanding</li><li>Car parks, surfacing &amp; line marking</li><li>Drainage &amp; SuDS attenuation</li><li>Boundaries, gates &amp; perimeter security</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What matters</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Built around your<br>building.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Built for scale and speed</span></h4><ul><li>Fast-track programmes geared to handover</li><li>Large-span access, MEWPs &amp; lifting plans</li><li>Live, 24/7 operations kept running</li><li>Phased around inbound &amp; outbound logistics</li><li>Big-box coordination across all four trades</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Compliance, handled</span></h4><ul><li>CDM 2015 throughout</li><li>Building Regs Part B (fire) &amp; Part L</li><li>BS 7671 electrical certification</li><li>BS 5534 fixings &amp; large-span roofing standards</li><li>SuDS drainage design to CIRIA C753</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you deliver fast-track industrial programmes?</summary><p>Yes. Big-box units are programme-led, so we pin long-lead items at design stage and run a buildable, phased programme with one project manager accountable for the handover date.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work in live, operating warehouses?</summary><p>Yes. Most refurbishment and upgrade works are phased around live logistics — out-of-hours isolations, temporary services and zoned working — so inbound and outbound operations keep moving while we work.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover EV charging and power upgrades?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver sub-mains, distribution and EV charging infrastructure, all certified to BS 7671 — from a handful of bays to fleet-scale charging and incoming-supply upgrades.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you handle large-span roofing and recladding?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver large-span roofing, overcladding and recladding with the right access and lifting plans, fixed and weatherproofed to BS 5534 and upgraded to meet Part L.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span class="ol-nm">MEPH</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial Fit-out</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Landscaping</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{@site.url}}/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Sectors", "item": "{{@s